summary: A Nord that looks like a wood elf.
descriptionHtml:
I tried to make a Nord look like a cute little wood elf. Why? Because Nords are easy to work with in RaceMenu. 

[size=3][b]Requirements: [/b][/size]
[list=1]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] for UNP with installer's optional add-ons (Eyes, Freckles, Brows, makeup, etc.) 
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url] - the hairs used.
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?#content]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] (make sure this overwrites Fair Skin's eyes!)
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] - duh.
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54118/?]The Neith Team Warpaints Set[/url] - to get the face paint (otherwise you'll have purple face!)
[*]SG Eyebrows
[/list][size=3][b]Recommended:[/b] [/size]
[list=1]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/63920/?]Test HDT Earrings[/url] - some nice earrings!
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57198/?]TDN Equipable Horns[/url] - to get the horns from the screenshots!
[*]My UUNP Bodyslide Preset - "[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85202/?]Dangerous Curves[/url]" - will look quite nice with this character!
[/list][b][size=3]Installation:[/size][/b]
[list=1]
[*]Download and extract my files.
[*]Main Skyrim Folder > Data > SKSE > Plugins > CharGen (This is where the sculpt files go).
[*]Now go into the presets folder that is within the CharGen folder - (This is where the jslot racemenu preset will go).
[/list]
author: wnisewond
